==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Offshore
<hw>Off"shore"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>From
the shore; <as>as, an <ex>offshore</ex> wind; an <ex>offshore</ex>
signal.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Located in the waters near the shore; <as>as,
<ex>offshore</ex> drilling</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Operating or located in a foreign country; <as>as,
an <ex>offshore</ex> bank account; <ex>offshore</ex> mutual
funds</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>offsides</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>offside</ent>⟦br⟧
